org.forgerock.openam.cors

Class CORSConstants

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.cors.CORSConstants

  • public final class CORSConstants
extends Object
    Holds all the necessary constants for the CORS Filter. Includes both keys for the configuration, as well as strings used throughout the CORS protocol.
